{"tid":525250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"抒情而震撼心靈的舞台　IU獲「韓國葛萊美」最高殊榮","createTime":"2018-01-10T12:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T09:29:34.000Z","uid":34643,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e948ed8c67bae06d81aecd89e1ddf59e3dbbea18","tid":525250,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;第32屆金唱片頒獎典禮（數字音源部門）&rdquo;在日山KINTEX5號館舉行。韓國金唱片大獎被譽為「韓國葛萊美」，IU作為最後一組主人公獲得&ldquo;第32屆金唱片頒獎典禮（數字音源部門）&rdquo;本賞後，帶來了《秋日早晨》、《夜晚的信》兩首歌曲的精彩表演舞台。美輪美奐的舞台效果配上IU干淨清爽的嗓音，為現場以及屏幕前的觀眾帶來絕佳視聽的享受，震撼心靈！最後頒發最高榮－－數位大獎則由韓國「可愛教主」IU獲得，她同時也獲得本獎，是最大贏家，全場歡聲雷動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/01/10/8435a6fb1a26316625e9bafc03b1c5af1515581369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F8435a6fb1a26316625e9bafc03b1c5af1515581369.jpg&h=5dbc52a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU是10年以來首次拿下金唱片音源大賞的女歌手，她謙虛致謝所有喜愛專輯《夜信》的人，尤其是作曲、作詞家辛苦付出心力，才能讓專輯有好的發展成績。話峰一轉，她向主持人李昇基提問「我還可以再說一點嗎」，聲音微微顫抖著提起日前自殺身亡的鐘鉉：「其實我現在還是很傷心，一位我所珍愛的朋友、音樂家先行離開了。我在某個程度中，可以理解那位（鐘鉉）為何會感到疲憊、痛苦，所以現在還是覺得難過、還有感到抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3044/d3044002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3044%2Fd3044002.jpg&h=02d25d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然不只IU，在場也有很多人抱著與IU一樣傷心的情緒，她最後安慰大家：「開心時大聲笑，傷心時哭出來，肚子餓的話就吃，也希望大家能夠讓這些自然而然發生的事情流露出來以及接受它。」最後她祝賀當天所有得獎的人：「希望大家可以睡個好覺，我也會那樣的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6235f945214ec7ff075a6bd95dd0041cafa4879d","tid":525250,"uid":85163,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92ef7cacf58fbf83393d2029b01aa707221f60a0","tid":525250,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:20:51.000Z","msg":"衰妹著到咁密實"},{"pid":"0432c78d1f6d2dd558c063795954cd63a810a1fb","tid":525250,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"solo世代到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/8b511c18ly1fnbq551ccbj20u01hcgqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F8b511c18ly1fnbq551ccbj20u01hcgqs.jpg&h=3b6b8298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/8b511c18ly1fnbq55en2sj20u01hc7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F8b511c18ly1fnbq55en2sj20u01hc7b9.jpg&h=4c5f5bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/8b511c18ly1fnbq5p4x6rj20qo0qowg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F8b511c18ly1fnbq5p4x6rj20qo0qowg4.jpg&h=700ba9b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6377fc6313f0d0388de6d19758050958b7698d10","tid":525250,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/005HZzCNly1fnbp5gu30vj30ku0kxtan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F005HZzCNly1fnbp5gu30vj30ku0kxtan.jpg&h=beb32757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b65294e363430d6e846347a64e5a1cc24885956b","tid":525250,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fnbo87x19oj30by0dgdgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fnbo87x19oj30by0dgdgv.jpg&h=53ea2293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb8b5053463316909048bb89b240a40d7029db09","tid":525250,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"cute<br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4721/24743872027_b2b1316f07_n.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4721%2F2474387